{"tid":1557223,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[不割蓆既極致！！］每樣文宣同我多謝每位手足！","createTime":"2019-09-10T04:34:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T05:21:58.000Z","uid":178548,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fbb72bdd83ffe436cb9fb35473379065b7f74dd4","tid":1557223,"uid":178548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T04:34:14.000Z","msg":"最近好多分化post<br />\n最近好多人都唔開心<br />\n最近好多指責post<br />\n但記唔記得我地話過<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">不指責、不割蓆、不篤灰</span></span><br />\n<br />\n屌人既說話聽完會嬲會傷心<br />\n讚美說話無人會嫌多<br />\n多啲講多謝唔會少忽肉<br />\n但可以係極大既鼓勵<br />\n<br />\n我希望以後<br />\n每個連登post<br />\n每份文宣<br />\n甚至係連儂牆<br />\n夜晚鳩叫<br />\n都可以加多句<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">多謝每一位手足嘅付出</span></span><br />\n<br />\n或者一句感激既說話<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n多謝每一位手足既付出"},{"pid":"22095f08b107ede1d4ada80df7e3a74470080536","tid":1557223,"uid":178548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T04:35:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0d556cb6ed82f70fbe908c380056c8597fe2924a","tid":1557223,"uid":178548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T04:35:49.000Z","msg":"推2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a1c45143375fcca420a28c334818719f46a9e9b","tid":1557223,"uid":178548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T04:36:04.000Z","msg":"推3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c2e7f2225f0776e87fe2f34e66a9e2501d793b7","tid":1557223,"uid":178548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T04:36:16.000Z","msg":"推4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84736b4f0d12e6a36a3a19b3eede4242d1890272","tid":1557223,"uid":178548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T04:36:28.000Z","msg":"推5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81435e680